Belén Rueda https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bel%C3%A9n_Rueda 0 María Belén Rueda García-Porrero (born 16 March 1965) is a Spanish actress. She is best known for her roles as Lucía in the TV series Los Serrano; as Julia in The Sea Inside, for which she won a Goya Award; and as Laura in The Orphanage, for which she received another Goya Award nomination. Most recently she played the lead role in the movie Julia's Eyes. María_Belén_Rueda_García-Porrero ( born_16_March_1965 ) is a_Spanish_actress .
